description:
Kueski is a leading platform in Latin America, offering fast and convenient personal loans up to $25,500 MXN without the need for a credit card or bank account. With Kueski, users can easily apply for loans online and receive instant approval, making it a perfect solution for those in need of quick financial assistance.
<br><br>
Converts on completed loan application.
<br><br>
Targeting:Men and women aged 25 to 59, socioeconomic level AB C+, interested in loans, expenses, finances, investment, savings, money, and family
<br><br>
Restrictions: Exclude the following domains from the sends:
@mail.com
@gmx.com
@proton.me
@protonmail.com

